      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "It is the twelfth-largest country in Europe by area, covering 238,397 km2 (92,046 mi2), and the sixth-most populous member state of the European Union, with 19 million inhabitants.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Romania",
